# Date          | Author | Version | Description
# 2016-06-27    | DNE    | 1.0     | BSI_UNMATCH subprog added
# 2016-07-05    | Bader  | 1.0     | FIND_OPEN_ITEMS: skip open items only if they are selected (DUDSEL = 2)
# 2016-07-08    | Bader  | 1.0     | CHECK_AMOUNT: set GCURLEG before ESC_AGIO
# 2016-07-12    | DNE    | 1.0     | BSI_MATCH_STATEMENT
