# 2016-08-09    | Bader  | 1.0     | SET_MATCHING_FLAG: call SET_BSIIMPD for all kinds of matches (not only "A")
# 2016-08-18    | Bader  | 1.0     | SET_MATCHING_FLAG: prevent writing of DUD fields to BSIIMPD for B and C hits
# 2016-09-13    | Bader  | 1.0     | HANDLE_SRC_DOC: add "Break" when returning due to INV00 overflow
# 2016-09-20    | Bader  | 1.0     | CHECK_AMOUNT: handle tolerance check correctly
